  "text": "Recall that it has been shown in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] that linear combination and composition of a finite number of ReLU DNNs can be realized by a ReLU DNN with polynomial complexity. Moreover, the identity function can be implemented as a ReLU network with one hidden layer. The precise statements of these results will be given in Appendix A for completeness.",
